ca.cgjennings.ui.textedit.completion

Interface CNode<T extends CNode>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the specific node type of the node's children
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    APILeaf, APINode, ClassNode, DefaultCNode, PackageNode, PackageRoot

    public interface CNode<T extends CNode>
    This interface describes a node in a tree of completion alternatives. The name CNode, which stands for "completion node", helps to differentiate from other kinds of nodes that implementations might have to deal with, such as AST nodes, flow graph nodes, etc.
    Since:
    3.0
